WEBVTT

00:55.097 --> 00:58.183
He spent the carnival trying to win me
one of those giant bears.

00:58.267 --> 01:02.312
{\an8}Spent all his money, has really bad aim.

01:02.396 --> 01:05.691
{\an8}All he ended up with
was this consolation prize.

01:06.692 --> 01:11.113
{\an8}Then I thought to myself,
maybe he's my consolation prize.

01:11.196 --> 01:13.615
I'm moving to New York
for college and dreams,

01:13.699 --> 01:17.411
and he's playing <i>Halo</i>
and contemplating a penis tattoo.

01:17.494 --> 01:20.247
So I just said it.

01:20.330 --> 01:22.291
"Maybe we should break up."

01:22.374 --> 01:25.586
And I was expecting him to say,
"No, I can't live without you, Lucy."

01:25.669 --> 01:28.922
But instead, he said, "Maybe you're right."

01:29.923 --> 01:31.425
And that was it.

01:31.508 --> 01:35.345
Now all I have left of our love is this sad,
second-place duck.

01:35.429 --> 01:37.681
And all his worldly possessions.

01:37.764 --> 01:39.558
Lucy, is this his retainer?

01:39.641 --> 01:42.769
He used to take it out
when we'd make out or have a snack.

01:42.853 --> 01:44.313
My favorite memories.

01:44.396 --> 01:46.565
He needs this. He has a shark mouth.

01:46.648 --> 01:48.317
Don't listen to Amanda.

01:48.400 --> 01:52.446
Your collecting is quirky and adorable.
You're basically an anthropologist.

01:52.529 --> 01:53.989
Correct, Nadine.

01:54.072 --> 01:56.575
I live in a cave of souvenirs,
like <i>The Little Mermaid.</i>

01:56.658 --> 01:59.161
- Nothing wrong with being sentimental.
- Sentimental?

01:59.244 --> 02:03.165
It was sentimental when we were 12.
This is full mental.

02:03.248 --> 02:04.958
A bike tire?

02:05.042 --> 02:07.002
Okay, this is active trash.

02:08.002 --> 02:09.794
What the hell?

02:09.880 --> 02:13.550
- A used condom?
