02:27.814 --> 02:30.984
Let's wait outside of the liquor store
for someone to buy us a box of wine.

02:31.068 --> 02:33.987
- And then drink it through Twizzlers.
- Yes!

02:34.071 --> 02:35.739
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

02:36.740 --> 02:38.033
Wait, are these his car keys?

02:41.370 --> 02:42.412
Vroom, vroom, bitch.

04:15.339 --> 04:17.507
Lucy, we're leaving.

04:20.052 --> 04:21.678
{\an8}Lucy, let's go!

04:22.679 --> 04:24.223
Lucy!

04:29.937 --> 04:32.272
- Found it.
- What's happening, <i>Grey Gardens?</i>

04:32.356 --> 04:35.150
Guest list for the Meszaros opening
at the gallery tonight.

04:35.234 --> 04:37.986
If I lost this, Eva would skin me alive.

04:38.070 --> 04:41.823
- Okay, she can't possibly be that scary.
- She's terrifying.

04:41.907 --> 04:45.160
Eva Woolf is the most influential gallerist
in New York.

04:45.244 --> 04:48.330
- As your lawyer, I'm saying, calm down.
- Well, you're not a lawyer.

04:48.413 --> 04:49.831
You're in law school.

04:49.915 --> 04:53.377
Whatever. I can still defend myself
when I murder Jeff.

04:53.460 --> 04:55.254
- <i>I love you.</i>
- Maybe one day,

04:55.337 --> 04:57.339
our paths will cross again.

04:57.422 --> 05:02.427
Look at that little baby model.
She has no idea she's an endangered species.

05:02.511 --> 05:05.180
Are you gonna marry Yulia
and get her a green card?

05:05.264 --> 05:09.059
Destiny has other plans for us.
Maybe we'll meet in another life.

05:09.142 --> 05:11.937
- Does she know that? Oh, God.
- That I believe in reincarnation?

05:14.648 --> 05:17.568
- Well, I saw that coming.
- You know what else I love about Max?

05:17.651 --> 05:19.653
Oh, please. We're waiting with bated breath.

05:19.736 --> 05:21.738
Ignore her. She hates joy and confetti.

05:21.822 --> 05:25.534
