05:48.348 --> 05:51.476
- Sorry.
- Just can't believe he chose little old me.

05:51.560 --> 05:54.730
- That literally makes no sense.
- Are you joking? You are a literal goddess.

05:54.813 --> 05:57.858
Are you guys exclusive? Have you discussed?

05:57.941 --> 06:01.653
