08:41.395 --> 08:46.193
Close your mouth, person.
It's unbecoming. Up, up, up.

08:46.276 --> 08:49.154
Oh, wait. Excuse me,
Mr. Sexpot Gallery Director?

08:49.238 --> 08:53.575
Hot tip, Marlene Dumas?
Focus on her riskier works.

08:53.659 --> 08:56.995
