in a woman's life,

09:39.496 --> 09:43.959
and I think you're unconsciously
subjugating yourself to prop him up.

09:44.042 --> 09:47.296
- <i>Classic overachiever.</i>
- <i>She seems really smart.</i>

09:47.379 --> 09:49.715
So we had this art opening
at the gallery tonight,

09:49.798 --> 09:53.218
which is why I'm an absolute vision.

09:53.302 --> 09:55.429
