so I didn't let her get to me.

10:41.725 --> 10:44.520
- Hello...
- Eva.

10:44.603 --> 10:48.440
- You.
- Hello, goddess, you, also.

10:48.524 --> 10:51.693
I'm not one of those bitches
that doesn't empower women.

10:51.777 --> 10:55.280
